Now it will be transformed to a WAN server (This will expose your IP address, be safe :)

1. Log into your router to Port Forward the server:

2. Look for Port Forwarding or New Rule
Internal IP: Choose your server IP
Protocol: TCP
Internal & External Port 25565

3. Go to: https://whatismyip.com (check your public ip)

4. Server Address to join will be: [public IP address]:25565

